    "type": "ContextOfUse",
    "name": "TPS tile surface temperature during re-entry",
    "description": "A CFD aerothermal model predicts peak surface temperature on TPS tiles during atmospheric re-entry to verify thermal margin. Model influence is HIGH (primary basis for TPS sizing); decision consequence is HIGH (under-prediction could lead to TPS failure).",
    "intendedUse": "Predict peak TPS tile surface temperature during re-entry trajectory to verify thermal margin exceeds 150K above predicted peak.",
    "modelRiskLevel": 3
  },
