    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Model deemed credible for TPS thermal margin prediction. All 19 factors assessed under NASA-STD-7009B. Key gaps in discretization error (achieved 2 vs required 3), model form (achieved 2 vs required 3), and results uncertainty (achieved 2 vs required 3) are mitigated by conservative thermal margin policy (150K above predicted peak).",
